{"tid":1312133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港良心）想讚下呢兩位警察先生 全部連登仔見到個post都入黎睇下","createTime":"2019-07-13T12:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T14:22:24.000Z","uid":9566,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9a46c5203c69c4338b53e77c8e14f2807d756c","tid":1312133,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"PC2664 武神上身 追住走緊既人黎打<br />\n想讚下佢情商夠高 知道啲人越退越要打 就算見到隔離啲傻鳩同事停晒手㩒住自己都無放棄繼續舉棍追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b-heQ0AZ3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb-heQ0AZ3&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=320c5de3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b-heQ0AZ3</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢位無名英雄 雖然搵唔到佢number出黎讚揚<br />\n但係憑佢知道敵人弱點 追住啲無裝備既人打 <br />\n打殘晒啲弱質對手先 智商取勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/videos/307812079966535?s=1256773088&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkucampustv%2Fvideos%2F307812079966535%3Fs%3D1256773088%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=46cc56f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/videos/307812079966535?s=1256773088&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位連登仔一齊讚揚下佢地 希望識佢地既人可以幫手話埋比佢地屋企人知 佢地光宗耀祖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不過要叫佢地小心啲 香港人並唔係弱者<br />\n下次必定以牙還牙 以眼還眼</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3b72f07414d86820f52ea1df08d6da4821c7e7f7","tid":1312133,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"起底"},{"pid":"ba9e4ed